    {
      "block_index": 10,
      "block_type": "paragraph",
      "text": "\n            This handbook describes the operational baseline for a multi-format\n            document conversion platform. It focuses on repeatable execution,\n            readable output, bounded fallbacks, and evidence-driven change\n            control rather than pixel-perfect visual reproduction.\n          ",
      "origin": {
        "format": "html",
        "source_name": "complex_html_documentation_site_page.html",
        "page": null,
        "slide": null,
        "sheet": null,
        "block_index": 10,
        "heading_path": null,
        "object_ref": "html:paragraph:11",
        "key_path": "$.html[11].paragraph"
      },
      "image": null
    },
    {
      "block_index": 11,
      "block_type": "paragraph",
      "text": "\n            Readers who only need the release checklist can jump to the\n            appendix, while implementers should also\n            review the external runbook\n            and the deployment contract.\n          ",
      "origin": {
        "format": "html",
        "source_name": "complex_html_documentation_site_page.html",
        "page": null,
        "slide": null,
        "sheet": null,
        "block_index": 11,
        "heading_path": null,
        "object_ref": "html:paragraph:12",
        "key_path": "$.html[12].paragraph"
      },
      "image": null
    },
    {
      "block_index": 12,
      "block_type": "blockquote",
      "text": "Stable structure beats optimistic heuristics when the source format\n            mixes headings, links, images, and noisy side material.",
      "origin": {
        "format": "html",
        "source_name": "complex_html_documentation_site_page.html",
        "page": null,
        "slide": null,
        "sheet": null,
        "block_index": 12,
        "heading_path": null,
